Anthrax - Sweden
--------------
Information received on 1 Nov 2013 from Dr Ingrid Eilertz, Chief Veterinary Officer Director and Head, Swedish Board of Agriculture Department for Animal Welfare and Health, Ministry for Rural Affairs, Jonkoping, Sweden

Summary
Report type: Immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 30 Oct 2013
